 {
  "text": "Hi, I am Bruno. Let me tell you about my free time. After work, I like playing games on my computer. On weekends, I love watching movies with my family. I do not like cooking, so my brother cooks for me. On Sunday morning, I like running in the park near my house. Running makes me happy. At night, I like reading a good book before I sleep. I have a lot of fun in my free time.",
