  "file": "a7_listening_bruno_freetime.mp3"
 },
 {
  "text": "Hello, my name is Carla. I want to tell you about my weekend. On Saturday, I like dancing with my friends. I love music, so dancing is my favorite hobby. I also like drawing. I draw pictures of my city. I do not like running, but I like walking in the park. On Sunday, I like cooking lunch for my family and watching a good movie. My weekend is always fun and busy.",
